(1) Write [npm help] For Show The Usage Of NPM

(2) Usage Of NPM Commands (Syntax)
-----------------------------------
==> npm + Command

EX
-----
==> npm install -h   // Shows The Different Ways That You Can Use 'install' Command
==> npm help-search update // Search In NPM Documentation About 'update' Keyword
==> npm help update // Will Open The Section Of 'update' Keyword In The NPM Documentation

